cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual attribute recognition and analysis from image-text data. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an automatic approach to discover and learn a classifier using neural activations in deep networks. 
3. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is another possible category as the paper deals with analyzing text data along with images. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing image-text data on the Web. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper deals with discovering and analyzing visual attributes from a noisy collection of image-text data on the Web.
